  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Complete denture wearer

          -  healthy

          -  ability to comply with the experimental protocol

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Candidiasis (thrush)

          -  use of antifungals, antibiotics or mouthwashes in the prior 3 months

          -  limited motor activity

          -  unhealthy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
